    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388440/extras/87fec8ae95016843e157d32aa3039d98.avif?t=1764615731\" width=600 height=76 /></span><br>Create and customize your own Battlecore with a wide variety of pieces and components. Axes that launch the enemy through the air, cluster bombs, homing bullets, moving traps... The possibilities are almost endless!<br> <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388440/extras/de28dc5b6152b2f2dc26c0f446055605.poster.avif?t=1764615731\" width=600 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388440/extras/de28dc5b6152b2f2dc26c0f446055605.webm?t=1764615731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388440/extras/de28dc5b6152b2f2dc26c0f446055605.mp4?t=1764615731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388440/extras/c699e56584fc023c448d9cc294a6085f.avif?t=1764615731\" width=600 height=76 /></span><br>Frantic battles await you throughout a large list of diverse arenas with unique mechanics. Battle alone against AI or with friends (up to 4 players) in local and online multiplayer via Steam Remote Play.<br> <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388440/extras/22ece76b970521a617b2cbb4e6025382.poster.avif?t=1764615731\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388440/extras/22ece76b970521a617b2cbb4e6025382.webm?t=1764615731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388440/extras/22ece76b970521a617b2cbb4e6025382.mp4?t=1764615731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388440/extras/3184994d64a5fe06d2303a6d2cb5fb5c.avif?t=1764615731\" width=600 height=76 /></span><br>Progress through the story and unravel the secret of Battlecore while unlocking new customizable pieces. Modify your equipment to match your opponent or let your imagination run wild and have fun surprising your friends with crazy combinations.<br> <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388440/extras/43159752bfb75d9c83719feec2c7fb27.poster.avif?t=1764615731\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388440/extras/43159752bfb75d9c83719feec2c7fb27.webm?t=1764615731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388440/extras/43159752bfb75d9c83719feec2c7fb27.mp4?t=1764615731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388440/extras/6638df53ad5515ed62f96a1436ccefdc.avif?t=1764615731\" width=600 height=76 /></span><br>The future of Battlecore is bright and exciting!:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Leaderboards<br></li><li>New Maps<br></li><li>New Gamemodes<br></li><li>New Skins<br></li><li>New Pieces<br></li><li>New Battlecores</li></ul><br>Will you take the reins of battle and remain the last one standing? Claim your place among the best!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388440/extras/938b7f90b7689979b5c54bbfd73ada5e.poster.avif?t=1764615731\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388440/extras/938b7f90b7689979b5c54bbfd73ada5e.webm?t=1764615731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388440/extras/938b7f90b7689979b5c54bbfd73ada5e.mp4?t=1764615731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Trailer music: Radio Rocket by PC-ONE - Free Music Archive - CC BY",
